def main():
    t = input()
    for i in range(int(t)):
        n = int(input())
        notes = 0
        if n >= 100:
            remain = n % 100
            notes = notes + (n - remain) // 100
            n = remain
        if n >= 50:
            remain = n % 50
            notes = notes + (n - remain) // 50
            n = remain
        if n >= 10:
            remain = n % 10
            notes = notes + (n - remain) // 10
            n = remain
        if n >= 5:
            remain = n % 5
            notes = notes + (n - remain) // 5
            n = remain
        if n >= 2:
            remain = n % 2
            notes = notes + (n - remain) // 2
            n = remain
        if n >= 1:
            remain = n % 1
            notes = notes + (n - remain) // 1
            n = remain
        print(notes)
